      "title": "Teenage boy drowns in Rideegama",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); A teenage boy had died after drowning in Ogodopola Mahayaya Canal in Rideegama.",
        "Police stated that the student met with the tragedy while swimming with a group of children.",
        "The deceased was identified as a 16-year-old resident of Polgolla.",
        "Police say that this group of students were on their way back after visiting a school in the Gokarella area for a sports competition, when they subsequently drowned in the canal after attempting to go swimming.",
        "Will support from Opposition until Tamil people are satisfied: C.V. Wigneswaran"
